						—Psalm 69:30
				</p>
				<section class = "separation-2"></section>
				<p class = "indent">
					Have you had a long and busy week? Are you going through difficult times? Or do you have reason to be joyful and thankful? We invite you to join us for Praise Night, a time of worship music and prayer held on Friday night. 
